er; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;跟我一起&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;听一下主创团队背后的故事吧~&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;作词者说&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); text-shadow: rgb(219, 238, 243) 2px 2px 10px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;接到填词任务是在一个疲乏的上午，当天凌晨我刚完成《渭上》------我的第一本书的初次修改。来不及缓和被&ldquo;起承转合&rdquo;弄得迟钝麻木的大脑，又要去作几句&ldquo;晓风残月&rdquo;的慨叹了。我一直把歌词当做白话诗来写， 加之少许古诗词的笔法。精妙不敢去想，只求没有生硬。关于离别，前人有无数佳句华章，我写起来实在是有点羞惭胆怯。所以这首诗里，有济慈和徐志摩，也有毫无灵气的我。临近毕业，我的&ldquo;骊歌&rdquo;，唱响在十里外的长亭边。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;演唱者说&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); text-shadow: rgb(219, 238, 243) 2px 2px 10px;&quot;&gt;酒吧驻唱三年有余，对音乐，从热爱到成为生命中最重要的一部分。非常荣幸能为枣院唱这首歌，也非常感谢我的好兄弟郑捷远和张玉良帮我吉他伴奏和手鼓伴奏。拿到词后，了解到这是一首关于毕业的歌，每个人都对毕业有独特的感觉，或喜或悲，所以这次演唱我分为两种基调，把A段的伴奏改成吉他和弦分解弹奏出来透露着淡淡的忧伤迎合了毕业的主调，而B段我则加入了手鼓和扫弦，展现了欢快的一面；这样既符合了毕业的伤感，也显示出踏出校门面向社会的喜悦和向往。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); text-shadow: rgb(219, 238, 243) 2px 2px 10px;&quot;&gt;最后，祝各位即将毕业的师哥师姐们毕业快乐，记得常回家看看。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); text-shadow: rgb(219, 238, 243) 2px 2px 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2018-06-17 10:33:52');

